text: Neustrelitz is a town in the south of Mecklenburg-Western Pomerania and the old capital city of the grand duchy Mecklenburg-Strelitz. Neustrelitz is 30 kilometers away from Neubrandenburg. About 21,000 people were living there in 2016. Category:Towns in Mecklenburg-Western Pomerania
title: Neustrelitz
